trans-unit.source: Provides a type converter to convert <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange"></xref> objects to and from various other types.
trans-unit.target: Fornece um conversor de tipo para converter <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange"> </xref> para e de vários outros tipos de objetos.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange> class represents a single date or a range of dates.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange>classe representa uma única data ou um intervalo de datas.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange>

trans-unit.source: This class is commonly associated with the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar> control, where it represents the selected and highlighted dates.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe é comumente associada com o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar>controlar, onde ele representa as datas selecionadas e realçadas.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.MonthCalendar>

trans-unit.source: The SelectionRangeConverter class is an adjunct class to <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange> that enables you to convert to and from other types, most often strings.
trans-unit.target: A classe SelectionRangeConverter é uma classe complementar para <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange>que permite que você converter para e de outros tipos, cadeias de caracteres com mais frequência.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange>

trans-unit.source: For more information about type converters, see the <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter> base class, [Generalized Type Conversion](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md), and [How to: Implement a Type Converter](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações sobre conversores de tipo, consulte o <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter>classe base [conversão do tipo generalizada](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md), e [como: implementar um conversor de tipo](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).</xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRangeConverter> class is specialized to convert between the types <xref:System.String> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange>.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRangeConverter>classe é especializada para converter entre os tipos <xref:System.String>e <xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRange> </xref:System.String> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.SelectionRangeConverter>
